  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Succor to the Most Vulnerable through Expansion of Local Resources.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A lot of efforts have been made by Caritas Nigeria for awareness creation and sensitization of the public on the mission and vision of the Organization. 
While there is little or no control on the gradual decline in foreign funding, it becomes utmost important to increase the fundraising drive and strategies that will boast ownership of the organization by Nigerians thereby fostering independence.

Therefore, the main focus is to increase our internally generated funds through donor acquisition, retention and upgrade, thereby rendering support to the most vulnerable in Nigeria and the world.</narrative>
  </description>
